text: Mădălina Ion (born 23 February 1996) is a Romanian handball player who plays for Universitatea Cluj-Napoca. ==Achievements== *Cupa României: **Winner: 2019 *Liga Națională: **Silver Medalist: 2019 *Supercupa României: **Finalist: 2018 *Supercupa României: **Finalist: 2018 *IHF Junior World Championship: **Bronze Medalist: 2016 *IHF Youth World Championship: **Gold Medalist: 2014 ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Bucharest Category:Romanian female handball players
title: Mădălina Ion
